## 2.0.0

### Breaking

- Upgraded the package to support Optimizely CMS 13, replacing the previous CMS 12 integration.
- Refactored virtual text routing to use CMS 13 application APIs such as `IApplicationRepository`, `IApplicationResolver`, and `RoutingEntryPoint` instead of site definition-based APIs.

### Added

- Added `ApplicationEventsSubscriber` so virtual text partial routers are registered when routable applications are created or updated.

### Changed

- Updated the test website to the CMS 13 stack, including ASP.NET Identity UI, Visitor Groups, and database compatibility configuration.
- Removed the direct `System.Linq.AsyncEnumerable` dependency and refreshed package locks to align with the CMS 13 dependency set.
